 PHASE 2 DESIGN: Design for Phase II portion of study: The MTD or a recommended phase 2 dose (RP2D) for the combination (80mg/m2 bendamustine) was identified in 2016, the plan is to treat additional patients at that dose to assess efficacy and response to treatment.

 The investigators plan to enroll 19 patients (including those treated at the MTD in Phase I).

